      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWILIGHT SLEUTH (1) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 22.15 with a 3 length win at this track over 390m. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Expected to be right there at the finish again. POWER AFFECT (2) lines up chasing another win after scoring over 390m at Warrnambool in 22.36, set up by a fast early sectional. Won at his only start from this draw. Can make it back-to-back wins. NICKLEBY ACTION (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (26.25) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Key runner on best form. BROADWAY ICON (7) was in the money last start at a short quote - likely to feature again.",
